{"tid":1641013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美球迷募資 號召NBA開幕戰穿挺港黑衣對抗支那","createTime":"2019-10-09T08:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T10:35:25.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1559682bb2e6ee378763e037ed5e18a6cf5a3752","tid":1641013,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ek1AhsL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEk1AhsL.jpg&h=94f898cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國職籃NBA休士頓火箭總經理摩瑞發表挺港推文引發熱議，有美國球迷在網路發起募資，希望NBA開幕戰當天，號召球迷穿上挺港黑色T恤。<br />\n<br />\n摩瑞（Daryl Morey）在推特發文支持香港反送中運動，而NBA總裁席佛（Adam Silver）也支持摩瑞言論自由，讓中國官媒中央廣播電視總台央視體育頻道決定暫時停播NBA賽事。<br />\n<br />\n有美國球迷發起募資活動，預計在22日（美國時間）開幕戰洛杉磯湖人與洛杉磯快艇交手的當天，在陣中球星詹姆斯（LeBron James）對戰雷納德（Kawhi Leonard）比賽前，將在主場史泰博中心（Staples Center）外發送印製「STAND WITH HONG KONG（挺香港）」字樣的黑色T恤，並附上小卡解釋穿上這件衣服的理由。<br />\n<br />\n發起人目標募資2萬美元（約新台幣62萬元），若未能達到目標，將全數退還；而若有多餘的資金，將繼續推動在其他球場外發送挺港黑色T恤活動，或捐給香港民間人權陣線。截至中午為止，募資活動引發熱烈響應，募資金額已超過4.3萬美元（約新台幣134萬元）。"},{"pid":"8299f529037b00c3863906bdd96fff3fc46a9a14","tid":1641013,"uid":230544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:16:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7dbe360a708681ced8e1502a6785c5f14e6f750b","tid":1641013,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/09/5mfi7t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F09%2F5mfi7t.jpg&h=bca3d389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}